text.section:
An individual authorized under subsection (a) of this section shall serve a summons to appear before a court-martial by:
delivering a copy of the summons to the offender;
reading a copy of the summons to the offender;
leaving a copy of the summons at the offender's last known residence or place of business; or
mailing a copy of the summons to the offender's last known residence or business address.
